# â­ **Deployment Strategies (Must Know for Interview)**

## **1) Rolling Deployment**

Server 1 â†’ update
Server 2 â†’ update
Server 3 â†’ update
â€¦
Old version slowly replace hota hai.

ğŸ¯ **No downtime**

---

## **2) Blueâ€“Green Deployment**

* Blue = current version
* Green = new version

Green test karo â†’ switch karo â†’ pura traffic green pe.

ğŸ¯ **Super safe**

---

## **3) Canary Deployment**

Pehle **5% users** â†’ test
Fir 25%
Fir 50%
Phir 100%

ğŸ¯ **Best for big companies**

---

## **4) Recreate Deployment**

Old version stop â†’ New version start

ğŸ¯ **Downtime hota hai**
Chota app ke liye OK

