# ğŸ›  **Deployment in Kubernetes (Very Important)**

Kubernetes me deployment =
**PODs ko manage karta**,
**auto-healing karta**,
**rolling updates deta**,
**rollback deta**.

Example:

```
kubectl apply -f deployment.yaml
kubectl rollout status deployment/myapp
kubectl rollout undo deployment/myapp
```

